ong D[4] value (and also wrong p[4] value) as DFS(0) goes deep 0 =E2=86=92 =
1 =E2=86=92 3 =E2=86=92 4 first, backtrack all the way to vertex 0 and even=
tually visit 0 =E2=86=92 2 but edge 2 =E2=86=92 4 cannot be processed as ve=
rtex 4 has been visited by DFS earlier.</p>

