slide-actions">DP(0)</span> works fast as the graph is actually a DAG, albe=
it having negative weight edge. As the graph is a DAG, there will not be an=
y negative weight cycle to worry about.</p><br><p>However, DP will not work=
 for any non DAG as non DAG contains at least one cycle and thus no topolog=
ical order can be found within that cycle.</p>

